                                <td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=30936&amp;sid=cfeccd1f2f7a24d55ad3e0a2ab8b1fa6#30936"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Wed Mar 17, 2004 3:09 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: OFFICIAL MAGIC SYSTEM INFO</span></td>
                                <td valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=30936&amp;sid=cfeccd1f2f7a24d55ad3e0a2ab8b1fa6"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>    </td>
